32
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:51,000
The first part of the bill seeks to amend section 28D and other relevant sections of the PAO to enable a certified public accountant practising.

33
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:55,860
To incorporate a company with only one director or shareholder.

34
00:06:56,380 --> 00:07:02,910
and register the company with the institute as a corporate practice qualified to perform audits.

35
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:08,700
Currently, under Section 28D of the PAO.

36
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:13,550
accountancy firms are permitted to incorporate a company with limited liability.

37
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:20,540
and register the company with the institute to provide audit services to public as a corporate practice.

38
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:34,460
Audits will be performed by those directors or shareholders of such a corporate practice who are certified public accountants holding a practising certificate issued by the institute.

39
00:07:35,690 --> 00:07:41,170
All directors and shareholders of corporate practices must be certified public accountants.

40
00:07:41,450 --> 00:07:47,240
In a proportion of whom must be certified public accountants holding practising certificates.

41
00:07:48,610 --> 00:07:52,950
under the pre-2003 companies ordinance situation.

42
00:07:53,610 --> 00:08:00,020
至少兩董事和股東是要求，為有限公司的註冊。

43
00:08:01,030 --> 00:08:06,390
As the corporate practice is a limited company, it had to meet this requirement too.

44
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:16,920
to enable sole practitioner firms to opt for incorporation, and at the same time satisfy the pre-2003 companies ordinance requirements.

45
00:08:17,450 --> 00:08:22,640
The P.A.O. allows the institute's council to permit a person.

46
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:27,400
Who is not a certified public accountant or a certified public accountant practising?

47
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:40,750
to become a director and nominee shareholder of a corporate practice with two directors or shareholders, if the other director or shareholder is a certified public accountant practicing.

48
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:52,900
The company's ordinance, Mr. Acting Chairman, was amended in 2003 to enable a single director and shareholder to incorporate a company.

49
00:08:53,500 --> 00:09:07,430
